OL,3,CDaughter inspired to join police after
OL,4,Cfather killed at sea
OL,6,FA woman whose father was killed at sea
OL,7,Fsays dealing with the police at such a
OL,8,Fdifficult time made her want to become
OL,9,Fan officer.
OL,11,FRebecca Michieli from Jersey lost her
OL,12,Ffather, Michael, as he was one of
OL,13,Fthree fishermen on board the L'Ecume
OL,14,FII trawler when it sank following a
OL,15,Fcollision with the Commodore Goodwill
OL,16,FCondor Ferry in December 2022.
