OL,3,CDaughter inspired to join police after
OL,4,Cfather killed at sea
OL,6,FAll three crew on board the smaller
OL,7,Fvessel died and the man in charge of
OL,8,Fnavigating the freight ship at the
OL,9,Ftime of the incident was jailed after
OL,10,Fbeing found guilty of breaking
OL,11,FJersey's shipping law.
OL,13,FRebecca says her father would want her
OL,14,Fto push to "something better" and
OL,15,F"stay positive" after a "hard three
OL,16,Fyears".
OL,18,FSo, she is one of the new recruits
OL,19,Fcurrently undergoing training with the
OL,20,FStates of Jersey Police.
