OL,3,CDaughter inspired to join police after
OL,4,Cfather killed at sea
OL,6,FSpeaking for the first time since the
OL,7,Fincident in an exclusive interview
OL,8,Fwith ITV News, Rebecca explains that
OL,9,Fher father would be proud of her
OL,10,Fdecision to help others.
OL,12,FShe adds: "My family went through a
OL,13,Fmajor incident and the police were
OL,14,Fjust everything we expected them to
OL,15,Fbe. They gave me a person to look up
OL,16,Fto, something that I wanted to be like.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
