OL,3,CDaughter inspired to join police after
OL,4,Cfather killed at sea
OL,6,F"It's something for me to focus on
OL,7,Fthat's positive and it doesn't feel
OL,8,Flike something is looming over me
OL,9,Fanymore, so it's given me something to
OL,10,Fwork towards."
OL,12,FRebecca had previously worked
OL,13,Falongside her father fishing and says
OL,14,Fthose memories will stand her in good
OL,15,Fstead for her new role.
OL,17,FShe explains: "I'm very practical,
OL,18,Fthanks to my Dad, so I think those
OL,19,Fsorts of skills, the late nights and
OL,20,Flong hours, are normal to me and will
OL,21,Freally help."
