OL,3,CDaughter inspired to join police after
OL,4,Cfather killed at sea
OL,6,FRebecca is one of ten new students to
OL,7,Fbegin a 20-week local training
OL,8,Fprogramme, where they will learn the
OL,9,Fskills and knowledge needed to become
OL,10,Feffective police officers.
OL,12,FOne of her training group is former
OL,13,FJersey Reds rugby captain, Lewis
OL,14,FWynne, who says his career as a player
OL,15,Fsets him up for this next step.
