OL,3,CDaughter inspired to join police after
OL,4,Cfather killed at sea
OL,6,FHe explains: "A lot of the
OL,7,Fphilosophies from rugby align well
OL,8,Fwith policing. It was always something
OL,9,FI wanted to do and the training we've
OL,10,Fdone over the past few weeks has made
OL,11,Fme want to be one more."
OL,13,FPaul Smith, Force Development Manager
OL,14,Ffor the States of Jersey Police, says
OL,15,Fthe recruits are "incredibly
OL,16,Fsignificant" and is grateful that all
OL,17,Ftraining can now take place on-island,
OL,18,Fwith students no longer needing to go
OL,19,Fto the UK for sections of the course.
