OL,3,CDaughter inspired to join police after
OL,4,Cfather killed at sea
OL,6,FHe states: "We really want to
OL,7,Frepresent islanders and the
OL,8,Fdemographics, so we have a wide range.
OL,9,FWe've had people from finance, rugby
OL,10,Fplayers, it's a really good mixture
OL,11,Fand now we're seeing the teamwork
OL,12,Fdevelop."
